trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> event is raised by the designer host for certain actions on a control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>denne hendelsen oppstår ved designer verten for visse handlinger på en kontroll i utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> is handled by a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> delegate method, which takes a ViewEventArgs object as a parameter.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>behandles av en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>delegere metode, som tar en ViewEventArgs-objektet som en parameter.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class supplies a default delegate to handle the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>Klassen gir standard representant til å håndtere <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Custom control designers override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnClick%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnPaint%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner.OnTemplateModeChanged%2A> methods to process those events for the control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Egendefinert kontroll utviklere overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnClick%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnPaint%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner.OnTemplateModeChanged%2A>metoder for å behandle disse hendelser for kontrollen i utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner.OnTemplateModeChanged%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnPaint%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnClick%2A>

trans-unit.source: The designer host initializes a ViewEventArgs object for the type of action on the design surface, and then passes the object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> delegate.
trans-unit.target: Spørringsutformer verten initialiserer et ViewEventArgs-objekt for type handling på utformingsoverflaten, og sender objektet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>delegere.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region%2A> property represents the control designer region that the event applies to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region%2A>egenskapen representerer kontrollen designer område som hendelsen gjelder.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A> property of the ViewEventArgs object indicates which type of action: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>for objektet ViewEventArgs angir hvilken type handling: – en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>hendelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> event.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A> property supplies the event arguments that are specific to the type of action.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A>egenskapen leverer argumentene hendelse som er spesifikke for type handling.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, the designer host initializes ViewEventArgs objects as follows: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs> object when you click a region.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel designer verten initialiserer ViewEventArgs objekter som følger: – en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs>objekt når du velger et område.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs> object when a control is drawn on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs>objekt når en kontroll tegnes på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs> object when the template editing mode changes for the control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs>objekt når malen redigeringsmodus endres for kontrollen i utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: For more information about events and delegates, see [NIB: Events and Delegates](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d98fd58b-fa4f-4598-8378-addf4355a115).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hendelser og representanter [NIB: hendelser og representanter](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d98fd58b-fa4f-4598-8378-addf4355a115).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs"></xref> class for the type of view event on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs"> </xref> klasse for hendelsestypen visningen på utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: The ViewEventArgs constructor is used by the designer host to initialize a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs> object for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> event.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren ViewEventArgs brukes av designer verten til å initialisere en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>objekt den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The designer host passes the initialized <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs> object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> delegate.
trans-unit.target: Spørringsutformer verten sender den initialisert <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>objekt i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>delegere.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Typically, `region` is set for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> events, and `null` (`Nothing` in Visual Basic) for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> events.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis `region` er angitt for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>hendelser, og `null` (`Nothing` i Visual Basic) for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>hendelser.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>

trans-unit.source: The type of action that raised the event; used to initialize the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType*>.
trans-unit.target: Hvilken handling som hendelsen; brukes til å starte <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType*>

trans-unit.source: The designer region that the action applies to; used to initialize the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region*>.
trans-unit.target: Spørringsutformer område som handlingen gjelder; brukes til å starte <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region*>

trans-unit.source: The event arguments associated with `eventType`; used to initialize the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs*>.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsen argumenter som er knyttet til `eventType`; brukes til å initialisere <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the event arguments that are associated with the action that raised the event.
trans-unit.target: Henter argumentene hendelse som er knyttet til handlingen som hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The EventArgs property supplies the event arguments that are specific to the type of action that is specified in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen EventArgs kan leverer argumentene hendelse som er spesifikke for type handling som er angitt i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, when you click a region, the designer host initializes the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A> as a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> event, and then initializes the EventArgs property as a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs> object.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel når du velger et område, designer verten initialiserer den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>som en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>hendelse, og initialiserer egenskapen EventArgs kan som en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>

trans-unit.source: Similarly, the designer host initializes the EventArgs property with a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs> object for a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> event, or a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs> object for a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: På samme måte designer verten initialiserer egenskapen EventArgs kan med en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs>objekt en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>hendelsen eller <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs>objekt en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>hendelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The EventArgs property is initialized by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen EventArgs kan initialiseres av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: An EventArgs that contains additional event data that is specific to the type of event.
trans-unit.target: En EventArgs kan som inneholder flere Hendelsesdata som er spesifikk for hendelsestypen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of action that raised the event.
trans-unit.target: Henter type handling som hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The EventType property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs> object indicates which type of action raised the event: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> event.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen hendelsestype for den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>objektet angir hvilken type handling hendelsen: – en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>hendelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> event.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A> property supplies the event arguments that are specific to the type of action.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A>egenskapen leverer argumentene hendelse som er spesifikke for type handling.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A>

trans-unit.source: The EventType property is initialized by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen hendelsestype er initialisert av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent"></xref> that specifies the type of action that raised the event.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent"> </xref> som angir type handling som hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the designer region that the event applies to.
trans-unit.target: Henter designer område som hendelsen gjelder for.

trans-unit.source: The Region property represents the control designer region that the event applies to.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen område representerer kontrollen designer område som hendelsen gjelder for.

trans-unit.source: Typically, the Region property is set for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> events, and `null` (`Nothing` in Visual Basic) for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> events.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis, område-egenskapen er angitt for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>hendelser, og `null` (`Nothing` i Visual Basic) for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>hendelser.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>

trans-unit.source: The Region property is initialized by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen område er initialisert av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion"></xref> that the action applies to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion"> </xref> som handlingen gjelder for.
